text: The Choco Mucho Flying Titans is a professional women's volleyball team playing in the Premier Volleyball League. The team is owned by Republic Biscuit Corporation. == History == The team was triumphant for their debut as they swept BaliPure Purest Water Defenders in their first game for the 2019 Premier
